{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Viewport","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Viewport","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>在电脑图形学里面，视口代表了一个可看见的多边形区域（通常来说是矩形）。在浏览器范畴里，它代表的是浏览器中网站可见内容的部分。视口外的内容在被滚动进来前都是不可见的。</p>\n<p>视口当前可见的部分叫做<strong>可视视口</strong>（visual viewport）。可视视口可能会比<strong>布局视口</strong>（layout viewport）更小，因为当用户缩小浏览器缩放比例时，布局视口不变，而可视视口变小了。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常规知识","title":"常规知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Viewport\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Viewport</a> 维基百科</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"在电脑图形学里面，视口代表了一个可看见的多边形区域（通常来说是矩形）。在浏览器范畴里，它代表的是浏览器中网站可见内容的部分。视口外的内容在被滚动进来前都是不可见的。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Viewport","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Viewport","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Vue","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Viewport (ビューポート)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"뷰포트","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Viewport","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Viewport","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Viewport","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/viewport","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/viewport/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Viewport","title":"Viewport"}],"pageTitle":"Viewport - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}